SUMMARY:LIFT Grant Program (BBOED)
DESCRIPTION:The Bayonne School District and the Bayonne Public Library 
 proudly present the “Bayonne Buzz Into Books” Program! Starting March 
 2nd\, join us for a twice weekly fun family story time led by a Bayonne 
 Board of Education teacher. Participating families get to take home free 
 books after each session to build their home libraries! This free program 
 is for families with children ages zero through three years old and will 
 run on Mondays from 4-5 pm and Fridays from 3:30-4:30 pm in the Small 
 Programming Room of the Bayonne Public Library. We hope to see you there!\n
LOCATION:Small Programming Room
