SUMMARY:May Afternoon Movies: The Night of the Hunter
DESCRIPTION:Save the dates! Join us at the Bayonne Public Library in the 
 Art & Music Room on the second floor every Wednesday this April at 1 pm for 
 a free movie! Each week\, we’ll be showing some of our favorite old and 
 new movies.  \n\n \n\nMay 6th - Song Sung Blue\n\nMay 13th - The Night of 
 the Hunter\n\nMay 20th - Elvis\n\nMay 27th - Patriots Day\n\n \n\nLight 
 refreshments will be served. We hope to see you there!
LOCATION:Art & Music
