SUMMARY:Chess Club (Ages 8-18)
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Bayonne Public Library for a Chess Club with Phil 
 Rosado! Phil is the author of “Mind Matter: Welcome to Chess!” This 
 weekly class for ages 8-18 meets from 6-7 pm in the Children’s Room. 
 Attendees will learn how to play chess and meet other novices. Advanced 
 registration is required for every session that you plan to attend. 
 Walk-ins will be included if space permits.\n\n\n\n
