SUMMARY:Tween & Teen Art Club: Create Your Own Jewelry With Izzy
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Bayonne Public Library on Thursday\, May 14th 
 from 6:30-7:30 pm for a night of fun with beads and elastic cord\, as you 
 make your very own jewelry from start to finish! All Art Club programs are 
 for tweens and teens ages 9-18 and will take place in the Art & Music Room 
 on the 2nd floor of the library. The supplies will be provided\, just bring 
 yourself and your creativity. Advanced registration is recommended\, but 
 not required. Walk-ins will be accommodated if space permits.
LOCATION:Art & Music
ORGANIZER;CN="Melody Scagnelli-Townley":MAILTO:mtownley@bayonnelibrary.org
