 5:45-6:45 pm in the Small Programming Room on the following 
 days:\n\n\n	February 25th\n	March 25th\n	April 29th\n	May 27th\n	June 
 10th\n\n\nWe hope to see you there!\n\nNo advanced registration is 
 required.
