SUMMARY:"PixelPop" Artist Alley Vendor Market
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Bayonne Public Library on Saturday\, May 30th 
 from 10 am to 3 pm in the Gallery for our “PixelPop” Artist Alley! 
 \n\nThis local vendor market\, hosted by @killjoyillustrations\, features 
 art from over 20 local artists and includes anime\, fan art\, trinkets\, 
 stickers\, keychains\, prints\, pins\, zines\, taxidermy\, crochet\, 
 jewelry\, and more! \n\nIt will be early internet throwback themed. It will 
 feature Y2K nostalgia as well as mid-90s and early 2000s vibes. There will 
 also be a free treat & craft table\, and cosplay is encouraged. This event 
 is free and family friendly!\n\n@sunspirecafe will also be there selling 
 espresso\, tea\, lemonade\, matcha\, and other drinks.\n\nCome support 
 local artists\, caffeinate yourself\, do some shopping\, and treat yourself 
 to something fun!
LOCATION:Gallery
