SUMMARY:Matcha Making Class with Sunspire Cafe
DESCRIPTION:Join the Bayonne Public Library and Sunspire Cafe on Tuesday\, 
 June 9th at 7 pm in the Gallery for a hands-on matcha making class! Learn 
 the fundamentals of matcha preparation while making your own Strawberry 
 Matcha Latte. Participants will take home their own matcha prep kit and 
 will receive some of Sunspire Cafe’s premium matcha to practice their 
 skills and recreate drinks at home!\n\nThis class is for ages 18 . Advanced 
 registration is required. Walk-ins will be accommodated if space permits. 
 Happy sipping!
