SUMMARY:Book a Librarian
DESCRIPTION:Do you need help with an online application?  Do you want to 
 set up an email account but don’t know how?  Do you need assistance with 
 tracing  your family tree? \n\nThe Bayonne Public Library is pleased to 
 announce a new service: Book A Librarian! Currently\, all appointments are 
 on Thursday evenings between 5:30 and 7:30 pm. \n\nBayonne patrons may 
 schedule an appointment for individualized assistance on a variety of 
 topics. \n\n \n\nWe can help with:\n\n\n	Online applications\n	Research 
 including local history & genealogy\n	Using Library resources such as 
 databases\, ebooks\, streaming TV & movies\, and Mango Languages\n	Setting 
 up an email account\n	Scanning & emailing a document\n	And many other 
 topics! \n\n\nPatrons with a valid Bayonne Public Library card may book one 
 45 minute appointment per month.\n\nPlease email refdesk@bayonnelibrary.org 
 or call 201-858-6980 to schedule an appointment.  Please include your 
 name\, email\, telephone\, library card number\, and the topic with which 
 you would like to receive assistance.
LOCATION:Classrooms C&D
ORGANIZER;CN="Bill Fischer":MAILTO:wfischer@bayonnelibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adults, Meeting, Seniors, Social Work, Tech Classes
UID:LibCal-17197-15951296
URL:https://bayonnelibrary.libcal.com/event/15951296
END:VEVENT
