SUMMARY:Evening Yoga Class
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Bayonne Public Library for Evening Yoga classes 
 with @imagineyogalucy! This is a bi-monthly Wednesday class from 7-8 pm in 
 the Gallery. This class will meet on the following days:\n\n\n	January 7th 
