SUMMARY:Anime Nights!
DESCRIPTION:Are you obsessed with anime\, manga\, and all things Japan? 
 Come hang out with us at the Bayonne Public Library with other fans who get 
 it! Whether you’re into action-packed shonen\, heart-melting rom-coms\, 
 or Studio Ghibli magic\, there’s a place for you here! \n\nNo 
 registration required\, but patrons MUST be ages 9-18.\n\nSave the dates 
 and join us for a night of otaku fun! Join us in the Art & Music Room on 
 the second floor twice a month on Thursdays from 6:30pm - 8:30pm! Snacks 
 ARE included! \n\n\n	May 21st\n	June 18th\n	July 9th\n	August 
 13th\n\n\nBring your friends\, your fandoms\, and your enthusiasm and 
 let’s geek out together!\n\n \n\nSummer Anime Movies: \n\nMay 21st: 
 Chainsaw Man - The Movie: The Reze Arc\n\nJune 18th: Dragon Ball Z: 
 Broly\n\nJuly 9th: Lupin the 3rd: The First\n\nAugust 13: Hunter x Hunter: 
 Phantom Rouge\n\n
