SUMMARY:Mortgage Support Tabling: The Waterfront Project
DESCRIPTION:Join the Bayonne Public Library and The Waterfront Project on 
 Thursday\, July 16th and Thursday\, July 23rd from 7-8 pm in the Lobby for 
 free mortgage support resources and assistance. \n\nRepresentatives from 
 The Waterfront Project will be available to provide reliable information\, 
 help you explore your options\, and connect you with resources that can 
 help you stay housed. \n\nNo advanced registration is needed. Just walk in 
 and you can receive assistance.\n
