SUMMARY:Toby and Friends Visit (Micro Highland Cows and Mini Baby Doll Lambs!)
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Bayonne Public Library on Tuesday\, July 21st at 
 6:30 pm for a fun and furry event: Toby and Friends! Meet Toby the micro 
 Highland cow along with his barn mates\, Baby Doll Lambs\, Storm and 
 Cloud\, for an extra special and memorable experience. Owner Ana will teach 
 us all about the world of miniature animal therapy and its benefits for 
 folks of all ages in places like hospitals\, schools\, nursing homes\, and 
 libraries. Attendees will have the chance for a photo opportunity with our 
 very special guests! Advanced registration is required\; walk-ins will be 
 accommodated if space permits. This event is open to all ages\, please 
 register all who will be attending. We hope to see you there!
LOCATION:Gallery
ORGANIZER;CN="Melody Scagnelli-Townley":MAILTO:mtownley@bayonnelibrary.org
