SUMMARY:Arts & Crafts (Ages 6-10)
DESCRIPTION:The Arts & Crafts program is on Thursdays from 3:15-4 pm. It is 
 for children aged 6-10 years old. Each week features themed crafts and 
 stories. No advanced registration is required. Spots will be filled on a 
 first come\, first served basis. We ask that parents of children under 9 
 years old remain in the room during the program.
