 The monthly puzzle group nights are drop-in and held on Thursdays from 6 to 
 8 pm in the Lobby of the Bayonne Public Library. Puzzle group nights will 
 meet on the following evenings:\n\n\n	February 12th\n	March 12th\n	April 
