SUMMARY:The Makery: Potato Press
DESCRIPTION:Are you curious about silkscreen printing? Discover the magic 
 of this amazing process and begin your journey from idea to beautiful 
 wearable art!\n\nJoin us at the Bayonne Public Library on Wednesday\, June 
 17th from 6:30–8:30 pm in the Small Programming Room for the first of two 
 parts of this inspiring Magical Monkey Makery workshop for ages 15 and up. 
 All materials are provided. \n\nWe will meet for the second part of this 
 workshop on Wednesday\, July 1st from 6:30–8:30 pm. \n\nBe sure to 
 register for and be able to attend both sessions to complete your creative 
 adventure. Registration is recommended\, but not required. Walk-ins will be 
 accommodated if space permits.
