DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Bayonne Public Library for free wellness 
 screenings\, courtesy of Hackensack Meridian Health! These screenings will 
 take place on Tuesdays from 3-5 pm\, in the Wellness Van (parked outside 
 the Bayonne Public Library)\, on the following dates:\n\n\n	July 
 29th\n	August 26th\n\n\nThe free tests will include blood pressure\, 
