 Dates for 2026\n\n \n\nTuesday\, January 6\, 2026 at 7:00 p.m.\n\nTuesday\, 
 February 3\, 2026 at 7:00 p.m.\n\nTuesday\, March 3\, 2026 at 7:00 
 p.m.\n\nTuesday\, April 14\, 2026 at 7:00 p.m.\n\nTuesday\, May 5\, 2026 at 
 7:00 p.m.\n\nTuesday\, June 2\, 2026 at 7:00 p.m.\n\nTuesday\, September 
 1\, 2026 at 7:00 p.m.\n\nTuesday\, October 6\, 2026 at 7:00 
 p.m.\n\nTuesday\, November 10\, 2026 at 7:00 p.m.\n\nTuesday\, December 1\, 
 2026 at 7:00 p.m.\n\n \n\nAll meetings will take place in the Board Room of 
 the Bayonne Public Library\, located at 697 Ave C\, Bayonne\, NJ 07002. 
 \n\n \n\nAll meetings are open to the public.\n
