SUMMARY:Intuitive Tarot Card Reading
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Bayonne Public Library for intuitive tarot card 
 reading classes for beginners!\n\nUnlock the power of tarot in this 
 beginner friendly class with Bayonne tarot card reader\, @tarot2thepeople! 
 You’ll learn how to interpret the imagery and symbolism of the cards to 
 spark your intuitive insights in order to start reading for yourself and 
 others. \n\nThis class will meet on the following Mondays at 7 
 pm:\n\n\n	January 12th & 26th\n	February 9th & 23rd\n	March 9th & 
 23rd\n	April 6th & 27th\n	May 4th & 18th\n	June 8th & 22nd\n	July 13th & 
 20th\n	August 10th & 24th\n	September 14th & 21st\n	October 5th & 
 19th\n	November 9th & 23rd\n	December 7th & 21st\n\n\nThis class is 
 intended for ages 18 and up. Advanced registration is required if you need 
 to borrow a tarot card deck. Walk-ins are permitted if you have your own 
 tarot card deck. No experience or materials necessary! \n\n \n
LOCATION:Small Programming Room
ORGANIZER;CN="Narissa Palmer":MAILTO:npalmer@bayonnelibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adults, Seniors, Teen Events
UID:LibCal-17197-15911698
URL:https://bayonnelibrary.libcal.com/event/15911698
