SUMMARY:Kidney Wellness Workshop
DESCRIPTION:This interactive class\, led by certified kidney care educators 
 will provide you with the knowledge to protect your kidney health. Whether 
 you are looking to prevent kidney disease\, manage existing conditions\, or 
 simply learn more about these vital organs\, this class is for you.
