SUMMARY:Jigsaw Puzzle Drop-In
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Bayonne Public Library for Puzzle Group Night! 
 The monthly puzzle group nights are drop-in and held on Thursdays from 6 to 
 8 pm in the Lobby of the Bayonne Public Library. Puzzle group nights will 
 meet on the following evenings:\n\n\n	February 12th\n	March 12th\n	April 
 9th\n	May 7th\n	June 11th\n	July 9th\n	August 13th\n	September 
 10th\n	October 8th\n	November 12th\n	December 10th\n\n\nPuzzles will be 
